\c 24
\s UDavida ubala abantu
\p
\v 1 Lwaselubuya lwamvuthela uIsrayeli ulaka lukaJehova\x + 21.1.\x*\x + 1 Lan. 21.1-28.\x*, wabavusela uDavida, esithi: Hamba ubale uIsrayeli loJuda\x + 1 Lan. 27.23,24.\x*.
\v 2 Ngakho inkosi yathi kuJowabi induna yebutho eyayilaye: Hamba khathesi ubhode ezizweni zonke zakoIsrayeli, kusukela koDani kuze kube seBherishebha, libale abantu ukuze ngazi inani labantu\x + 23.15. 3.10.\x*.
\v 3 UJowabi wasesithi enkosini: Aluba iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ingandisa ebantwini, loba bebanengi kangakanani, kuphindwe ngokulikhulu, ukuthi amehlo enkosi yami, inkosi, akubone. Kodwa inkosi yami, inkosi, ithokozelani kulinto\x + Dute. 1.11.\x*?
\v 4 Kodwa ilizwi lenkosi lalilamandla phezu kukaJowabi laphezu kwezinduna zebutho. Ngakho uJowabi lenduna zebutho baphuma phambi kwenkosi ukuze babale abantu, uIsrayeli.
\p
\v 5 Basebechapha iJordani, bamisa inkamba eAroweri\x + Dute. 2.36.\x*, ngakwesokunene komuzi ophakathi kwesifula seGadi, lamaqondana leJazeri\x + Nani 21.32.\x*.
\v 6 Basebefika eGileyadi lelizweni leTahetimi-Hodishi; bafika eDani-Jahani\x + Josh. 19.47. Hlu. 18.29.\x*, babhoda ngaseSidoni\x + Josh. 19.28. Hlu. 18.28.\x*,
\v 7 bafika enqabeni yeTire\x + Josh. 19.29.\x* lemizini yonke yamaHivi\x + Josh. 11.3. Hlu. 3.3.\x* leyamaKhanani\x + Josh. 11.3. Hlu. 3.3.\x*; baphuma baya eningizimu yakoJuda, eBherishebha.
\v 8 Sebebhode badabula ilizwe lonke, bafika eJerusalema ekupheleni kwenyanga eziyisificamunwemunye lensuku ezingamatshumi amabili.
\v 9 UJowabi waseyinika inkosi inani lokubalwa kwabantu; njalo kwakukhona koIsrayeli amaqhawe ayizinkulungwane ezingamakhulu ayisificaminwembili\x + 1 Lan. 7.2,4,5,7,9,40. 21.5.\x* ahwatsha inkemba\x + Hlu. 8.10.\x*; lamadoda akoJuda ayengamadoda ayizinkulungwane ezingamakhulu amahlanu.
\p
\v 10 Inhliziyo kaDavida yasimtshaya emva kokuthi esebale abantu\x + 1 Sam. 24.5.\x*. UDavida wasesithi eN\nd kosi\nd*ni: Ngonile kakhulu ngalokho engikwenzileyo. Ngakho-ke, N\nd kosi\nd*, ngiyakuncenga, susa ububi benceku yakho\x + 12.13.\x*, ngoba ngenze ngobuthutha obukhulu\x + 1 Sam. 13.13.\x*.
\v 11 Kwathi uDavida esevukile ekuseni, kwafika ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* kuGadi umprofethi\x + 1 Sam. 22.5.\x*, umboni kaDavida\x + 2 Kho. 17.13. 1 Lan. 21.9. 25.5. 29.29. 2 Lan. 9.29. 12.15. Amos 7.12.\x*, lisithi:
\v 12 Hamba uthi kuDavida: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* \add ithi\add*: Ngikubekela okuthathu; zikhethele okukodwa kukho, ukuthi ngikwenze kuwe.
\v 13 UGadi wasefika kuDavida, wamtshela wathi kuye: Kufike kuwe yini iminyaka eyisikhombisa yendlala elizweni lakini? Loba ubalekele izitha zakho inyanga ezintathu zixotshana lawe? Ingabe kube khona umatshayabhuqe wesifo okwensuku ezintathu elizweni lakini? Khathesi cabanga, ubone ukuthi yimpendulo bani engizayibuyisela kongithumileyo\x + 1 Lan. 21.12.\x*.
\v 14 UDavida wasesithi kuGadi: Ngicindezelekile kakhulu; ake siwele esandleni seN\nd kosi\nd*, ngoba izisa zayo zinkulu, kodwa kangingaweli esandleni somuntu.
\p
\v 15 Ngakho iN\nd kosi\nd* yasibeka umatshayabhuqe wesifo kuIsrayeli, kusukela ekuseni kwaze kwaba sesikhathini esimisiweyo; kwasekusifa ebantwini abantu abayizinkulungwane ezingamatshumi ayisikhombisa kusukela koDani kwaze kwaba seBherishebha\x + 24.2.\x*.
\v 16 Lapho ingilosi iselulela isandla sayo eJerusalema ukuyibhubhisa, iN\nd kosi\nd* yazisola ngalobobubi\x + Gen. 6.6. 1 Sam. 15.11. Jow. 2.13,14.\x*, yathi engilosini\x + 2 Kho. 19.35. Seb. 12.23.\x* eyayibhubhisa abantu\x + Eks. 12.13,23.\x*: Sekwanele. Khathesi finyeza isandla sakho. Ingilosi yeN\nd kosi\nd* yayisebaleni lokubhulela likaArawuna umJebusi.
\v 17 UDavida wasekhuluma eN\nd kosi\nd*ni lapho ebona ingilosi eyayitshaya abantu, wathi: Khangela, mina ngonile, njalo mina ngenze okubi; pho, lezizimvu zenzeni? Isandla sakho ake simelane lami njalo simelane lendlu kababa\x + 7.14.\x*.
\p
\v 18 UGadi wasefika kuDavida ngalolosuku, wathi kuye: Yenyuka, umisele iN\nd kosi\nd* ilathi ebaleni lokubhulela likaArawuna umJebusi.
\v 19 UDavida wasesenyuka njengokutsho kukaGadi, njengokulaya kweN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 20 UArawuna waselunguza, wabona inkosi lenceku zayo beqhubeka besiza kuye; uArawuna wasephuma wakhothama phambi kwenkosi ngobuso bakhe emhlabathini.
\v 21 UArawuna wasesithi: Kungani inkosi yami, inkosi, ize encekwini yayo? UDavida wasesithi: Ukuthi ngithenge kuwe ibala lokubhulela, ukuthi ngakhele iN\nd kosi\nd* ilathi\x + Gen. 23.8-16.\x*, ukuze inhlupheko ithinteke ingafiki ebantwini\x + 24.25. Nani 16.48,50.\x*.
\v 22 UArawuna wasesithi kuDavida: Inkosi yami, inkosi, kayithathe inikele lokho okuhle emehlweni ayo\x + 3.19. 10.12. 15.26. 19.18.\x*; bona, \add nanzi\add* inkabi zomnikelo wokutshiswa, lezimbulo\x + Isa. 41.15.\x* lezinto zenkabi kube zinkuni\x + 1 Kho. 19.21.\x*.
\v 23 Konke lokhu, nkosi, uArawuna wakunika inkosi; uArawuna wasesithi enkosini: IN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho kayikwemukele\x + Dute. 33.11.\x*.
\v 24 Inkosi yasisithi kuArawuna: Hatshi, kodwa ngizakuthenga lokukuthenga kuwe ngentengo; njalo kangiyikunikela iminikelo yokutshiswa engangibizanga lutho eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu wami. UDavida waselithenga ibala lokubhulela lezinkabi \w ngamashekeli\w** esiliva angamatshumi amahlanu\x + 1 Lan. 21.25.\x*.
\v 25 UDavida wasesakhela khona iN\nd kosi\nd* ilathi, wanikela iminikelo yokutshiswa leminikelo yokuthula\x + Hlu. 20.26. 21.4.\x*. Ngakho iN\nd kosi\nd* yancengeka ngelizwe\x + 21.14.\x*, inhlupheko yasithinteka phezu kukaIsrayeli\x + 24.21.\x*.
